---
/**
 * CommercialConsultingBlock.astro — answer-first SEO/AEO block for commercial consulting intent.
 * Targets AI consultant Oakville/GTA and e-commerce consultant searches without changing the service offer.
 */
---

<section id="ai-consultant-oakville" class="py-16 md:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-10">
      <p
        class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[#06b6d4]"
        style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;"
      >
        Quick answer for Oakville / GTA businesses
      </p>

      <h2
        class="mb-5 text-2xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#e6edf3] md:text-3xl"
        style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;"
      >
        Need an AI consultant in Oakville who actually builds the system?
      </h2>

      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.25fr_0.75fr] lg:items-start">
        <div>
          <p
            class="mb-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#c9d1d9]"
            style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;"
          >
            Greg Kowalczyk is an Oakville-based AI implementation and e-commerce consultant serving the GTA and Ontario. The work is practical: custom AI tools, Shopify and Amazon workflows, marketing automation, SEO/AEO systems, and operating dashboards that replace repetitive agency or staff work.
          </p>

          <p
            class="mb-5 leading-relaxed text-[#c9d1d9]"
            style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;"
          >
            If you are searching for an <strong class="text-[#e6edf3]">AI consultant in Oakville</strong>, a <strong class="text-[#e6edf3]">Shopify consultant for a small business</strong>, or someone who can connect e-commerce data to day-to-day automation, the first question is simple: what manual work should stop happening this month?
          </p>

          <p
            class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-[#8b949e]"
            style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;"
          >
            The proof is not a slide deck. It is the same ecosystem Greg is building in public: TapeGeeks for commerce, RunMate Pro for audience growth, Bronte Harbour Classic for community proof, and SportsClinicFinder for local search scale. Those projects feed the playbook used for client work.
          </p>

          <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5">
              <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[#e6edf3]" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">
                Best fit
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#8b949e]" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">
                Product businesses, Shopify/Amazon operators, local service businesses, and SMBs with manual workflows that are eating time or margin.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-5">
              <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[#e6edf3]" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">
                What you get
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#8b949e]" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">
                A working AI or growth system, clear documentation, and training so your team can run it without becoming dependent on another vendor.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="rounded-2xl border border-[#06b6d4]/25 bg-[#06b6d4]/[0.06] p-6">
          <h3
            class="mb-4 text-lg font-semibold text-[#e6edf3]"
            style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;"
          >
            Start here
          </h3>
          <ul class="mb-6 space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#c9d1d9]" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">
            <li><a class="text-[#06b6d4] hover:text-white" href="/news/ai-search-optimization-2026/">See the SEO/AEO ecosystem Greg is building</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-[#06b6d4] hover:text-white" href="/projects/">Review live projects and tools</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-[#06b6d4] hover:text-white" href="/contact/">Book a call about your AI implementation</a></li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="inline-block w-full rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl"
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;"
          >
            Book a Call
          </a>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
